creator: Shareasy Inc Pte Ltd
descriptionHtml:
FREE SIGN UP, NO DEPOSIT REQUIRED!

Brezze SG is the new sharing economy poised to disrupt the mobile technology business in Singapore. Borne out of a commonly experienced problem – battery depletion that comes with frequent mobile usage, Brezze SG provides battery charging solutions through unparalleled convenience and a plethora of usage benefits.


-Scan QR code on the Brezze SG station to collect your powerbank. Pay only for the rental duration.

-Charge and use while on the go, and return to any Brezze SG station when you are done.
